{"tid":824610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★iOS 瀏覽器最新漏洞　程式碼即令iPhone、iPad重新開機","createTime":"2018-09-17T06:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T03:22:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1a784a808d13864037d8ec931e8615edf9e9f7cf","tid":824610,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"九月 17, 2018<br />\n<br />\n最近有資訊安全人員表示，只需要 15 行程式代碼，即可讓使用 iOS 系統的裝置馬上重新啟動，而 macOS 上的 Safari 瀏覽器亦會受到有關攻擊影響。導致程式死機，沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n資訊安全研究人員 Sabri Haddouche 於 9 月 15 日，透過 Twitter 公布一個針對 iOS 裝置的攻擊程式。據 Haddouche 張貼在 GitHub上的程式看來，攻擊手法是利用 WebKit 的漏洞，在 CSS 背景上加入大量 &lt;div&gt; 指令。當受害者使用 iOS 進入包含有關代碼的網頁時，該代碼就會消耗裝置所有資源來處理有關指令，造成裝置核心錯誤（Kernel Panic），導致系統自動重新啟動。<br />\n<br />\n由於 Safari 瀏覽器同樣使用 WebKit 引擎，所以有關漏洞亦適用於 macOS 上的 Safari 瀏覽器。 Haddouche 向外國科技網站 Techurch 披露，攻擊代碼可以隱藏於 HTML 檔案之中。意味著如用家在社交網站或電郵上意外進入包含有關代碼的網頁時，都會導致裝置自動重新開機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/09/17/ios-css-attack/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2Fios-css-attack%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=ZeZ6tPDxC3becklY%2FXKFRBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4cddce70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/09/17/ios-css-attack/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"cbd9fe45b8379449093b1f8c35b86b4e353329ce","tid":824610,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"apple已死"},{"pid":"d3b249eb9835ae0a0b1a2ff42f365cccd8c45c0c","tid":824610,"uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/pwnsdx/ce64de2760996a6c432f06d612e33aea/raw/fb78440ee4bce427f0cde98a4e9feadfd9eed198/safari-reaper.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.rawgit.com%2Fpwnsdx%2Fce64de2760996a6c432f06d612e33aea%2Fraw%2Ffb78440ee4bce427f0cde98a4e9feadfd9eed198%2Fsafari-reaper.html&d=ZeZ6tPDxC3becklY%2FXKFRBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=244efdbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.rawgit.com/pwnsdx/ce64de2760996a6c432f06d612e33aea/raw/fb78440ee4bce427f0cde98a4e9feadfd9eed198/safari-reaper.html</a>"},{"pid":"23fa436e46db65ef0b1311fd3f343e3cff53421b","tid":824610,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"ios12有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7be4cb44cfff673f268c973aade0753fb662574","tid":824610,"uid":18641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:04:35.000Z","msg":"今次真係hack with html<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b98b1d8087af52ea91c215d5e0f34f9637d364","tid":824610,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b249eb9835ae0a0b1a2ff42f365cccd8c45c0c","tid":824610,"uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/pwnsdx/ce64de2760996a6c432f06d612e33aea/raw/fb78440ee4bce427f0cde98a4e9feadfd9eed198/safari-reaper.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.rawgit.com%2Fpwnsdx%2Fce64de2760996a6c432f06d612e33aea%2Fraw%2Ffb78440ee4bce427f0cde98a4e9feadfd9eed198%2Fsafari-reaper.html&d=ZeZ6tPDxC3becklY%2FXKFRBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=244efdbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.rawgit.com/pwnsdx/ce64de2760996a6c432f06d612e33aea/raw/fb78440ee4bce427f0cde98a4e9feadfd9eed198/safari-reaper.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5176e890be4eda7bd2426fb38a49072065aedf","tid":824610,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"IDOG又話好安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa